quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,238,"Observe prayers, especially the middle (afternoon) prayer, and stand you before Allah with full attention and devotion"
  2,239,"And if you stand in danger, then pray afoot or on horseback; but when you are in safety remember Allah, how He taught you what yet you knew not"
  2,240,"Those of you who die and leave wives, should bequeath to their wives maintenance for a year, without expulsion (from their home); but if they go out of their accord, there is no crime in you for what they do of their own rights. Allah is Mighty and Wise"
  2,241,"And divorced women should have a maintenance in reason, - a duty this on those that fear"
  2,242,Thus does Allah explain to you His revelations so that you may understand
  2,243,"Do you not look at those who left their homes by thousands, for fear of death; and Allah said to them \"Die,\" and then He quickened them again? Verily Allah is Lord of Grace to men, but most men give no thanks"
  2,244,"Fight then in the way of Allah, and know that Allah is both Hearer and Knower"
  2,245,"Who is there that will lend to Allah a goodly loan? He will increase it many times; Allah closes His hand and holds it out (i.e. He gives want or plenty), and unto Him shall you return"